http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/Five-day-school-festival-kicks-off/article13983780.ece

: The stage events of the district revenue arts festival got off to a colourful start as the programme was formally declared open at the government higher secondary school, the main venue on the second day here on Tuesday.The day progressed with staging of crowd pulling competitions like mono act, classical music, kuchipudi, light music, Arabic music, elocution and poem recital at the Municipal Town Hall and Chinmaya Vidyalaya.The other major events held during the day include oppana, mappilapattu, duff mutt, kolkali and arabana muttu.The five-day event will conclude on January 8.